        "subject": "LU-16518 build: disable Clang warnings on GNU C extensions",
        "message": "LU-16518 build: disable Clang warnings on GNU C extensions\n\nClang will complain about GNU C extension (which the\nkernel allows). Silence these warnings. This fixes the\n-Wgnu-variable-sized-type-not-at-end warnings seen in\nlustre_idl.h.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Ib7ccd676c39221cb058366c16271ab29ffdc1fc3\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62954\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
